<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Weinsberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen eines Urteils mit, dass eine Anhörung in der Fastenzeit an den üblichen Gerichtstagen Montag, Mittwoch und Freitag möglich ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_230" id="114v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l1">VVeinſperg / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l2">Lieben frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> frewnde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l3">cʒu vns ſchicken wöllet / von einer vrteil vvegen / vnd bittet das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l5">vvir ew 
<add><ab facs="#facs_230_line_1576589541956_4578"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab></add> vviſʒen laſʒen / vvenn vvir vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_230_r2l4">dartʒu </ab></add> gemüſʒigen <expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan> / laſʒen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l6">vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vviſʒen / vvenn die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> in der vaſten ſchierſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l7">cʒu vns komen ſo Rate iſt / ſo wöllen vvir ſie <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>horen</expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l8">
<add><ab facs="#facs_230_r1l1">darv̈mb <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>richten</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_230_r1l2">ſo vvir beſt mügen </ab></add> Auch laſʒen vvir ew vviſʒen / daʒ <expan>gevvönliche<ex>n</ex></expan> am Montag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l9">Mitvvochen / vnd am freitag Rate beÿ vns iſt / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>Sex<ex>ta</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_230_r2l10"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Kathedra Petri / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_230" id="114v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Weinsperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnde, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt, daz ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> frewnde czu uns schicken wöllet von
                        einer urteil wegen, und bittet, das wir ew
                                    <add><expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan></add> wiszen
                        laszen, wenn wir uns <add>darczu</add> gemüszigen
                            <expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan>, laszen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wiszen, wenn die
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> in der vasten schierst czu uns komen, so
                        rate ist, so wöllen wir sie <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>horen</expan> und <add>darümb
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>richten,</expan> so wir best mügen</add>. Auch
                        laszen wir ew wiszen, daz <expan>gewönliche<ex>n</ex></expan> am montag,
                        mitwochen und am freitag rate bey uns ist. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>sex<ex>ta</ex></expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> kathedra Petri.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
